'''''Frat Rock! The Greatest Rock 'n' Roll Party Tunes of All-Time''''' is a [[compilation album]] released by [[Rhino Records]] in 1988, featuring "[[frat rock]]" songs from the 1950s and 1960s. Different volumes of ''Frat Rock!'' were released on [[gramophone record|vinyl]] and [[CD]] both before and after this release.
