** Vatican City's sole armed forces, The [[Pontifical Swiss Guard|Swiss Guard]], is made up entirely of Swiss Catholics; however, Swiss Guards are granted Vatican citizenship while they serve.<ref>[[Pontifical Swiss Guard]]</ref>

